'''国际竹藤组织'''（{{lang|en|'''International Bamboo and Rattan Organisation'''}}，简称'''INBAR'''），是一个政府间的国际组织。

==历史==
成立于1997年11月6日，总部设在[[中华人民共和国|中国]][[北京|北京]]。国际竹藤组织是第一个由[[中华人民共和国|中国]]发起成立，且总部设在中国的[[国际组织|国际组织]]。国际竹藤组织的宗旨是致力于利用[[竹藤|竹藤]]资源提高社会、经济及环境的效益，通过竹藤产业帮助生活在有竹藤地方的人们消除贫困。截止2018年，已有44个国家接受INBAR的《成立协定》成为成员国。<ref>Eva Wollenberg, Andrew Ingles. ''Incomes from the Forest: Methods for the Development and Conservation of Forest Products for Local Communities''. CIFOR, 1998. {{ISBN|9798764196}}. Page 58.</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=-s0sAQAAMAAJ&q=%22International+Network+for+Bamboo+and+Rattan%22&dq=%22International+Network+for+Bamboo+and+Rattan%22&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y | title = Management and Utilization of Bamboo and Rattan in Papua New Guinea | author =  | date =  | accessdate = December 8, 2015 | publisher =  | language =  | archive-date = 2021-05-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210512024319/https://books.google.com/books?id=-s0sAQAAMAAJ&q=%22International+Network+for+Bamboo+and+Rattan%22&dq=%22International+Network+for+Bamboo+and+Rattan%22&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="About">{{cite web | url = http://www.inbar.int/this-is-inbar | title = This is INBAR | author =  | date =  | accessdate = December 8, 2015 | publisher =  | language =  | archive-date = 2015-12-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151210201502/http://www.inbar.int/this-is-inbar | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

